<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_4634c58a-c9ed-4f5e-8001-5c321d877249" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>C2P2</sptc><title id="_9930840b-c49f-4ba7-a5ec-07ad56878f20">Swimming pool drainage</title><archive-num>2019: CP2.2</archive-num><clause-variation variation="NT" variation-type="DELETE">NT DELETE Clause</clause-variation><subclause id="_44194680-8f5c-480d-9cb0-69f310bcebaa" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_cb0f2f7c-bfe6-4cc8-9014-d63ab74c1d23">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>An adequate means of draining a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_03b62055-01e0-4bf5-a89e-f6522a9b7bf9" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> must be designed and installed in a way that will not cause illness to people.</p></subclause><subclause id="_cb851e96-2ff7-4838-a81d-571ed58a908e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_f7426f38-71f0-488a-82d6-0e3afec456b2">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>An adequate means of draining a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_8212db51-c0b3-44d4-96fb-6534d1c130dc" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> must be designed and installed in a way that will not affect any <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1387_0.4.0.xml#_f